OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning cloud clearing to leave
OL,6,Fanother dry and sunny day. Some patchy
OL,7,Fcloud may return into the afternoon as
OL,8,Fthe sunshine turns a little hazy.
OL,9,FTemperatures a little lower than of
OL,10,Flate as winds turn northerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMost seeing clear spells
OL,13,Fovernight with intermittent areas of
OL,14,Fcloud. Winds dropping out and staying
OL,15,Fmild overnight, but more comfortable
OL,16,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
