OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloud lingering through the
OL,6,Fmorning and sticking around for much
OL,7,Fof the day. The odd shower may
OL,8,Fdevelop, but most places staying dry.
OL,9,FTemperatures slightly down compared to
OL,10,Frecently.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,13,Fdry into the second half of the
OL,14,Fweekend, with sunny spells by day and
OL,15,Fclear skies at night. Temperatures
OL,16,Ftrending a little nearer to average,
OL,17,Fbut still feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
